## Planning Rules (Summary)

1. Any architectural or refactor work MUST begin with a plan file.
2. Plans use templates from `docs/ai/templates/`.
3. Plans must include: File Impact Map, Tests, Execution Steps, Validation, Rollback.
4. Plan lifecycle: Draft -> Review -> Ready -> In Progress -> Complete.
{% if config.gates.review_to_ready.devils_advocate %}
5. Devil's advocate review required before execution.
{% endif %}
